{"tid":85386,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【你呃人！】「仲喺庫房度」？　文匯報：CY全捐六千元助中国人","createTime":"2017-01-18T09:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T10:24:19.000Z","uid":11001,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2681d1ec10969547e038d5c020a2c9501e6c81b","tid":85386,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:43:19.000Z","msg":"特首梁振英今日在施政報告後的記者會上，談全民退保時突然提到政府當年所派6,000元，他至今沒提取過，「仲喺庫房度」，更指自己「唔需要嗰6,000蚊」，似有意暗寸前財政司司長曾俊華。<br />\n<br />\n但翻查資料，2011年財政預算案向成年的永久居民派發6,000元現金，<span style=\"color: red;\">《文匯報》當時曾大篇幅報道，時任行政會議召集人梁振英曾在公開活動表示，他會把6,000元捐給「寸心行動」基金，協助受沙漠化影響的內地人。</span>當時「寸心行動」基金亦指善款在短短3個月內已達13萬元。梁振英當時亦呼籲中小學生，捐出部分利是錢。但今日記者會上，卻稱未有提取過6,000元，未知是否最終未有捐出款項。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170118/56189601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170118%2F56189601&d=HGH7WEzPWRAnxUgEFdg11Av3KisNQlPySkJrDkY9tT8%3D&h=745f31fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170118%2F56189601&h=cb1d4c06\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170118/56189601</a>"},{"pid":"8b15b07d0ad61fff5bb611fbb79b0d8f06d5ade1","tid":85386,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:46:25.000Z","msg":"究竟係走數定講大話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12caaff476a763d0a237eb384cc7d40f2e7a9730","tid":85386,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"你唔需要=所有人唔需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e13b391ca7892c3c26d1609517faf18d18ab5073","tid":85386,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T09:54:27.000Z","msg":"6000換五千萬，抵到<img src=\"/assets/face